<title>Site Updates [Sun, Jan 12, 2003 : 1930] :: V a z a e l l e . N E T :: The BEST Server In EverQuest&#8482;</title>
<meta http-equiv="Keywords" content="I'm,just,slightly,overdue,for,some,updates,so,here,goes,-,Layout,Changes,-,Bugs,in,the,Forums,-,Xorrin,returning,to,EQ,Layout,Changes,	As,you,can,see,there,are,some,minor,layout,changes,to,the,site,Most,noticeable,however,is,the,new,layout,of,the,Main,Menu,What,does,this,all,mean,It,means,BIG,changes,are,on,the,way,for,Vazaelle,NET,	The,original,plans,for,the,site,were,to,separate,everything,Vazaelle,NET,was,to,be,a,generic,site,for,the,Vazaelle,server,in,general,Back,in,the,days,before,Vazaelle,NET,2,sites,existed,nato-vazalle,for,the,Alliance,and,kgm-vazaelle,for,my,Guild,When,I,bought,this,server,I,had,problems,with,my,former,hosting,company,FREEBOOST,COM,The,owner,Jeff,refused,to,release,the,domains,to,me,even,though,I,owned,them,He,had,somehow,locked,them,with,his,registrar,even,though,I,owned,them,on,a,different,one,As,a,result,I,was,forced,to,register,a,NEW,domain,Vazaelle,NET,I,have,since,regained,control,of,nato-vazaelle,but,kgm-vazaelle,was,forever,lost,to,an,online,casino,–,bastards,	Since,I,own,the,server,I,decided,to,offer,free,web,space,to,any,NATO,Guild,who,needed,it,I,would,also,provide,web,space,to,other,EQ,sites,for,very,reasonable,rates,NATO,members,would,be,able,to,register,their,own,domain,Guilds,from,the,Vazaelle,server,would,also,have,the,ability,to,use,a,sub-domain,when,linked,from,the,Vazaelle,NET,site,Vazaelle,NET,would,be,home,to,the,generic,site,for,the,Vazaelle,server,as,a,whole,KGM,Vazaelle,net,would,be,home,to,the,Knights,of,the,Green,Mist,guild,site,NATO,Vazaelle,NET,would,be,home,to,the,Norrath,Alliance,Treaty,Organization,site,NATO,members,would,be,able,to,use,URLs,such,as,nv,vazaelle,net,thor,vazaelle,net,and,rov,vazaelle,net,Each,site,would,be,completely,separate,from,the,other,	So,what,does,this,have,to,do,with,the,menu,you,ask,Simple…,It’s,the,first,step,in,separating,the,NATO,and,KGM,sites,The,software,that,this,site,runs,on,PostNuke,PN,supports,Multi-Site,installations,What,this,allows,the,developer,to,do,is,tie,certain,aspects,of,the,different,sites,together,while,still,keeping,the,core,separate,For,example,users,would,register,at,Vazaelle,NET,or,any,sub-site,This,single,registration,would,carry,to,all,other,instances,of,the,PN,chain…,one,registration,one,log-in,Then,each,separate,site,Admin,could,define,permissions,for,that,particular,site…,thus,allowing,the,Admin,for,xyzguild,vazaelle,net,to,promote,his,users,permissions,while,not,affecting,the,permissions,of,the,same,user,on,abcguild,vazaelle,net,or,nato,vazaelle,net,Pretty,nifty,huh,So,why,wait,for,PN,8,0,rather,than,moving,forward,with,the,7,2,x,upgrade,Security,for,one…but,the,main,reason,is,functionality,The,PN,developers,have,saved,the,BEST,new,features,for,the,8,x,rollout,Bugs,in,the,Forums,	Been,getting,a,lot,of,questions,about,configuration,customization,and,general,use,of,the,forums,lately,I've,also,been,noticing,a,lot,of,people,poking,around,in,areas,they,really,shouldn't,be,This,really,isn't,a,major,issue,but,does,warrant,some,attention,	First,customization/features,The,forums,are,run,using,phpBB,1,14,I,have,spent,TONS,of,time,and,energy,researching,and,trying,out,the,MANY,different,bulletin,board,packages,out,there,I've,even,considered,ezboards,but,decided,that,they,really,did,need,to,be,an,actual,part,of,the,site,I,boiled,my,final,choices,down,to,2,systesm,ikonboard,and,phpBB,I,personally,like,the,ikonboard,better,as,far,as,overall,features,go,but,it,does,not,play,well,with,other,features,of,the,site,and,the,administration,of,it,is,a,little,sloppy,phpBB,offered,simpler,navigation,and,just-as-powerful,features,plus,it,tied,in,perfectly,with,the,site,right,down,to,using,the,site,theme,in,stead,of,having,to,build,a,new,one,from,scratch,to,make,it,match,The,only,problem,is,at,the,time,the,site,was,installed,and,in,my,haste,to,get,the,forums,up,and,running,before,I,moved,to,the,other,side,of,the,planet,the,version,that,got,installed,was,not,complete,We,are,currently,running,a,&quot,beta&quot,of,sorts,it,is,a,100%,from-scratch,rewrite,of,phpBB,specifically,for,PostNuke,-,NOT,a,port,of,an,already,working,system,meant,to,stand,alone,This,allows,more,functionality,and,integration,with,the,core,PN,site,ie,You,register,and,log,in,once,rather,than,once,on,the,site,and,again,on,the,forums,It,also,ties,directly,in,to,the,user,security,system,-,access,and,permissions,making,user,administration,easier,Version,2,of,phpBB,has,all,that,are,currently,allowing,everyone,to,see,read,and,post,in,any,forum,regardless,of,their,access,level,fixed,and,will,be,installed,in,the,next,upgrade,to,the,site's,core,software,What,I,ask,of,you,for,now,is,to,please,be,patient,with,the,forums,and,please,do,not,post,where,you,don't,belong,Specifically,-,if,you,are,not,a,member,of,the,Alliance,Council,a,guild,leader,of,a,NATO,member,guild,please,do,not,post,there,Xorrin,returning,to,EQ,	I,wish,Ok,so,I,FINALLY,get,my,computer,after,the,movers,lost,everything,I,own,for,4,months,And,it,even,made,it,here,AFTER,the,Typhoon,so,it's,not,damaged,I,managed,to,save,up,the,money,to,get,PoP,and,SoV,for,my,2nd,account,in,all,I,spent,over,$400,in,EQ,software,upgrades,alone,thanks,to,the,high,cost,of,living,here,Each,copy,was,$134,plus,a,few,extra,toys,I,picked,up,remember,that,little,PayPal,donation,button,on,the,main,page,*lol*,Happy,Birthday,to,meeeeee,*hint*,yes,today,is,my,B-day,for,real,Now,all,I,have,to,do,is,get,connected,to,the,internet,right,Hrmm,	If,it,were,that,easy,I,would,have,been,online,on,Friday,You,see,the,phone,company,says,they,can,&quot,hook,me,up&quot,within,2,hours,of,me,calling,them,That,is,if,the,phone,line,is,working,BUT,since,my,house,took,a,lightening,strike,some,time,before,I,moved,into,it,ALL,the,phone,lines,are,fried,We're,talking,crispy,black,lines,that,turn,to,dust,when,you,touch,them,And,not,just,the,lines,inside,yes,every,outlet,in,every,room,but,also,the,box,on,the,side,of,the,house,the,lines,under,ground,going,to,the,main,junction,box,for,the,street,and,yes,even,insde,the,junction,box,itself,All,of,it,-,fried,-,needs,to,be,replaced,	No,big,deal,I,can,do,that,in,a,weekend,*IF*,I,could,find,a,place,on,this,island,that,sells,spools,of,phone,line,and,connection,boxes,Why,won't,the,phone,company,do,it,They,will,in,May,or,June,for,$80/hour,They,only,maintain,the,lines,going,from,their,switch,TO,the,junction,box,not,the,box,itself,or,anything,between,it,and,your,phone,on,the,wall,remember,that,nifty,little,PayPal,donation,button,on,the,main,page,Happy,birthday,to,meeee,have,I,mentioned,how,expensive,stuff,is,here,on,Guam,*hint*,Really,I,hate,to,beg,but,it's,pretty,bad,out,here,anything,helps,even,$5,I'm,already,paying,over,$150,just,to,maintain,this,web,site,lol,not,to,mention,my,monthy,EQ,fees,which,I,cannot,play,In,the,3+,years,I've,been,playing,EQ,I,think,I've,only,been,able,to,actually,get,on,it,about,2,of,them,even,though,I've,been,paying,all,along,/sigh,think,Verant,will,pay,the,phone,company,to,fix,me,up,lol,They,can,afford,it,Oh,DSL,to,be,hooked,up,within,1,week,of,the,phone,getting,turned,on,depends,on,how,long,it,takes,the,ISP,to,do,their,paperwork,since,the,phone,company,was,sued,by,AT&amp,T,and,cannot,sell,DSL,to,the,public,Did,you,know,AT&amp,T,doesn't,even,exist,on,Guam,Nifty,how,they,can,do,that,huh,I,had,more,to,write,but,forgot,it,all,lol,look,for,an,edit,some,time,when,my,brain,returns,to,me" />
